import {createRouter,createWebHashHistory} from "vue-router";
const routes=[
    {path:'/',redirect:'/Index'},
    {path: '/Index', component: () => import('src/Views/Index.vue'),},
    {path: '/Blog', component: () => import('../src/Views/Blog.vue'),},
    {path: '/Login', component: () => import('../src/Views/Login.vue'),},
    {path: '/Register', component: () => import('../src/Views/Register.vue'),},
    {path: '/Self', component: () => import('../src/Views/Self.vue'),},
    {path:'/Follow',component:()=>import('../src/Views/Follow.vue')},
    {path: '/Fixing',component:()=>import('../src/Views/Fixing.vue')},
    {path: '/Release',component:()=>import('../src/Views/Release.vue')},
    {path: '/Collection',component:()=>import('../src/Views/Collection.vue')},
    {path: '/Search',component:()=>import('../src/Views/Search.vue')},
    {path: '/ChangePassword',component:()=>import('../src/Views/ChangePassword.vue')},
    {path: '/ChangeName',component:()=>import('../src/Views/ChangeName.vue')},
    {path: '/Video',component:()=>import('../src/Views/Video.vue')},
    {path: '/Master/user',component:()=>import('../src/Views/Master_user.vue')},
    {path: '/Master/type',component:()=>import('../src/Views/Master_type.vue')},
    {path: '/Master/blog',component:()=>import('../src/Views/Master_blog.vue')},
    {path: '/test',component:()=>import('../src/Views/test.vue')},
]
const router=createRouter({
    history:createWebHashHistory(),
    routes,
})
export default router
